              </div>
              <h3>Gold Jewellery</h3>
              <p>Timeless gold necklaces, bangles, rings and earrings crafted in 18K, 22K and 24K purity.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" width="44" height="44"><circle cx="32" cy="32" r="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="32" cy="32" r="10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="14" y1="32" x2="22" y2="32" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="42" y1="32" x2="50" y2="32" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3>Silver Jewellery</h3>
              <p>Sterling silver with intricate detailing — from contemporary minimalist to traditional Nepali patterns.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" width="44" height="44"><polygon points="32,10 42,26 58,28 46,40 48,56 32,48 16,56 18,40 6,28 22,26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3>Diamond & Gemstone</h3>
              <p>Certified diamonds and precious gemstones — perfect for engagements, anniversaries and gifting.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" width="44" height="44"><path d="M20 12Q32 6 44 12L48 32Q40 52 32 56 24 52 16 32Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3>Bridal Sets</h3>
              <p>Complete bridal jewellery from Naugedi to Tilhari — designed for your special day.</p>
